**Race:** :: Vampire, formelly human\par
**Age:** :: Appears mid-20's (undead)\par
**Values:** :: Obedience to Azalin Rex, maintaining order, loyalty, chain of command\par
**Personality:** :: Calculating, authoritative, and enjoys manipulating others\par
**Trait:** :: Elegant and composed, exuding an air of authority.\par
**Mannerism:** :: Speaks in a refined and commanding tone. Asks rethorical questions.\par
**Talent:** :: Vampiric abilities, great tactician\par
**Flaw or Secret:** :: Fears being replaced or degraded within Kargat\par
