**Base of Operations:** :: Cosmopolis Club in Martira bay\par
**Allies:** :: Kargat, Kargatane\par
**Enemies:** :: Enemies of Azalin Rex, Alanik Ray\par
:\par
**Vampiric Doom:** :: Doomed to die with her eyes exposed.\par
\par
